Purpose (What this step really is)

Define the Blueprint that determines:
documents, sections, requirements, validation rules, and AI behavior.

UI Title (recommended):

Document Blueprint Setup
Choose how your document structure and requirements are defined.

Option 1 ‚Äî Select Program (Funding / Bank / Investor)
What this REALLY does

Creates a Program-Based Blueprint

Program defines:

Required documents

Required sections

Validation rules

Evidence requirements

Formatting rules

Scoring logic

UI Content (EXACT)
Card Title:

Select Funding Program

Description:

Choose a funding, bank, or investor program. We will automatically apply the required documents, sections, and compliance rules for this program.

What user sees when clicking:
A. Program Input

