Option 2 ‚Äî Use Own Template (Upload)
What this REALLY does

Creates a Template-Based Blueprint

Template defines:

Initial structure

Headings

Formatting
NOT compliance

UI Content (EXACT)
Card Title:

Use Own Template

Description:

Upload your own DOCX or PDF. We will extract the structure and use it as your starting document layout. You can still add program requirements later.

What user sees when clicking:
A. Upload Area

Upload DOCX / PDF

Show detected:

Documents

Headings

Styles

TOC presence

B. Structure Preview

Tree preview of detected structure

Mapping confidence

Unmapped headings

C. Optional Overlay Toggle

‚¨ú Add program requirements later

